Thomas D. TAYLOR, Plaintiff-Appellant, v. The TULSA TRIBUNE COMPANY, Defendant-Appellee. No. 189. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Feb. 7, 1938. Enos S. Booth, of New York City (Harris Jay Griston, of New York City, of counsel), for appellant. Peaslee & Brigham, of New York City (Gerald J. McMahon and Dexter Brigham, both of New York City, of counsel), for üefendant-appellee.

Before MANTON, SWAN, and AUGUSTUS N. HAND, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order affirmed.
